{"tid":1933133,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【武漢肺炎】21歲男疑病毒襲神經線致肌肉萎縮 武漢醫生揭停止血清檢測 所有個案「清零」","createTime":"2020-03-19T06:25:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-19T10:05:31.000Z","uid":13663,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f3b1b1891d9d616df874cec3e1cddfabd01a280a","tid":1933133,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T06:25:10.000Z","msg":"有曾駐守方艙醫院的武漢醫生回覆指，就其目前所知，亞洲心臟病醫院和湖北省人民醫院均已經停止血清檢測，他估計武漢已經全面喊停，連同濟與諧和兩間醫院也做不了。他說，你可以想像這背後的原因，這和醫學沒有任何關係，都是「政治學的診斷」、「政治學的治癒」。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全文：<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200318/BB2NYR6SGPFQJWC5YEKHG6BRZ4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200318%2FBB2NYR6SGPFQJWC5YEKHG6BRZ4%2F&d=vBgtTLCpkGvyAljQauEZFZE%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=770d7e76\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200318%2FBB2NYR6SGPFQJWC5YEKHG6BRZ4%2F&h=ce2b5589\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200318/BB2NYR6SGPFQJWC5YEKHG6BRZ4/</a>"},{"pid":"5bf646e0c1613dfaafcf6b7fe87916546e44c448","tid":1933133,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T09:25:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1642ea65844a6d797f23127be91e683b7ff5d88a","tid":1933133,"uid":23697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T09:41:06.000Z","msg":"沒事兒"},{"pid":"12b78c243cdb2f5b1054b48362edb9da1c3edb6f","tid":1933133,"uid":160147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T09:56:15.000Z","msg":"支持佢繼續隱瞞<br />\n大陸繼續歌舞昇平<br />\n繼續聚餐聚會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70ea7e26514027a14b8301c5c092871b332ee157","tid":1933133,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T10:05:31.000Z","msg":"好叻<img src=\"/assets/faces/n